    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once nearly cooked through, add the <strong>sun-dried tomato butter </strong>to the pan and swirl the pan around until the butter has melted and is foaming</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (not sure about citrus? Try using less!)</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the prawns are cooked through – these are your <strong>Spanish-style king prawns</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
